Installing
==========

`Text::FindLinks` is a Perl module for automatic URL markup and extraction. To
install:

    $ perl Build.PL
    $ ./Build
    $ ./Build test
    $ ./Build install

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command: `perldoc Text::FindLinks`.

